# Cline / Roo Code Rules — Gai Framework (github.com/Hlgxz/gai)
#
# AI-native Go web framework. Setup: go mod tidy && go build ./...
#
# CRITICAL: Always import github.com/Hlgxz/gai/http as ghttp.
# Handler signature: func(c *ghttp.Context).
# ORM uses generics: orm.Query[T](db), orm.Get[T](q), orm.Create[T](db, &item).
# Models embed orm.Model with gai:"..." struct tags.
# Routes: r.Get("/path/:param", handler), r.Group(), r.Resource().
# Middleware: return ghttp.HandlerFunc, call c.Next().
# Validation: ghttp.NewValidator(data, rules) with pipe syntax.
# Schema: YAML in schemas/ → gai generate --schema schemas/.
# Files: snake_case.go. Tables: auto plural snake_case.
# No init() outside database/driver/. Use ServiceProvider.
# See CLAUDE.md or AGENTS.md for full documentation.
